title: General Electric Dishwasher Lower Rack And Swb Replacement Kit
description: General Electric Dishwasher Lower Rack And Swb Replacement Kit ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 19 Reviews PartSelect Number PS16618974 Manufacturer Part Number WD28X28918 This dish rack is for dishwashers. Dish rack holds the dishes in place during the dish washing cycle

installationInstructions.author: Wilson from MENIFEE, CA
installationInstructions.title: upper and lower rack ASM showed sing of rust
installationInstructions.content: Repair was simple, lower rack just remove and replaced with out any tools or disassemble required, for the upper rack installation, the end cap need to be removed out of the sliding tracks, slide old rack out and discard, clean the track with a suitable cloth and slide new rack in to the tracks, reinstall the old end caps, as a good preventing measure, order new end caps just in case they are need it if the old ones crack during removal. save old rollers from old racks for future repairs
